name: R2-subscription-channel-type-for-R5
title: Cross-version VS for R2.SubscriptionChannelType for use in FHIR R5
description: This cross-version ValueSet represents concepts from http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/subscription-channel-type|1.0.2 for use in FHIR R5. Concepts not present here have direct `equivalent` mappings crossing all versions from R2 to R5.
